Suspect value
note:
<SGType:1>    
<SGDescription:\I[94]About the Female Suspect Value

At the start of the game, the villagers mistake Hinori for a male.
However, depending on the player's actions, Hinori may begin to suspect that she is actually a "female."
The Female Suspect Value represents the degree to which the villagers suspect Hinori is female.
In Kakuriyo Village, it is a serious crime for a woman to pretend to be a man.
Please be careful not to let the value reach its maximum for Hinori's safety.
The Female Suspect Value can be checked on the map screen or the menu screen meter.

\I[37]Increase in Female Suspect Value
Actions taken with a libido of 50% or more, actions taken in the evening, feminine actions

\I[53]Decrease in Female Suspect Value
Resting at home, actions taken like a man

<SGCategory:Help>   // Name of the category to which the term belongs

note:
<SGType:1>    
<SGDescription:\I[93]About Estrus Value

This represents Hinori's level of estrus.
In the lewd and lustful Kakuriyo Village, even if Hinori is still sexually immature,
her desires gradually build up as she moves around outside.
The villagers are sensitive to the scent of a female.
If Hinori is in estrus while moving around, she will be immediately noticed.
When the estrus value is 50% or higher, the female exposure value will increase when talking to villagers.
Also, it is easier to encounter female exposure events while in estrus.

\I[37]Estrus value increases
Passage of time, encountering lewd events, and other events

\I[53]Estrus value decreases
Resting at home, hiding and doing lewd things

name: Days Passed and Days Remaining
note:
<SGType:1>    
<SGDescription:\I[193]Regarding the number of days passed and remaining

The village of Kakuriyo is connected to the present world once a year.
In other words, the next opportunity to return will be exactly one year from the day Hinori and Ao wandered into this village.

This game consists of 24 turns, which are divided into four seasons of summer, autumn, winter, and spring, each lasting six days.
The basic flow of this game is to raise the adult value of Hinori and Ao while being careful not to reveal their true identities until the 24 turns have passed, and to avoid being taken into the village.

>           // Explanation of the term (1)
<SGCategory: Help>   // Name of the category to which the term belongs.

name: Schedule
note:
<SGType:1>    
<SGDescription:\I[193]Daily Routine

In this game, you will mainly explore the village during the day.
You can explore in the morning/noon/afternoon/evening,
and you can continue to act in the evening.
However, in the evening, there are perverts lurking in Kakuriyo Village.

If you encounter them, Hinori may show a girlish reaction without thinking.

Let's go home as soon as possible when the sun goes down.

>           // Explanation of terminology (1)
<SGCategory:Help>   // Name of the category to which the terminology belongs.

name: Scenario Controls
note:
<SG:1>   
<SG:\I[193]Explanation of controls in the scenario.

In this game, the following shortcuts are available:
Hide conversation window... Right-click/PageDown/tab... Hide conversation window
Auto text advance... Shift
Skip... Hold down ctrl
Backlog... Mouse wheel up/hold down shift

Each function can also be accessed from the icon in the lower right corner of the conversation window.
The keyboard arrow keys, WASD, and mouse are all configured for one-handed operation during scenes.
Additionally, the speed of auto text advance can be changed from the options.
